#                 also authors fontkit (font subsetting), restructure
#                 (binary format parser), brotli.js, and most of the
#                 lower-level binary-format tooling that pdfkit
#                 composes on top of.  No other npm PDF library
#                 covers the full pure-JS write path from a layout
#                 builder API through font subsetting to a valid
