# Rust completion #229 (_paper-age) + Go completion #229 (_bas-celik) +
# TS-Node completion #229 (_afterwriting) = triple-229.  Axis #167
# closed in the lifetime of the corpus — every pure-language PDF
# generation library that produces a valid PDF 1.7 file directly from
# in-process layout primitives in the three big systems languages now
# has both a representative consumer completion AND a documented axis
